originContent: Foxel - 智能图像检索与管理系统
translatedContent: Foxel - Intelligent Image Retrieval and Management System

originContent: Foxel 是一个基于 .NET 9 开发的现代化智能图像检索与管理系统，集成先进的 AI 视觉模型 和 向量嵌入技术，提供高效的图像搜索与管理功能。
translatedContent: Foxel is a modern intelligent image retrieval and management system developed based on .NET 9, integrating advanced AI vision models and vector embedding technology, providing efficient image search and management functions.
> 🖥️ **Online Demo:**

originContent: > 访问 [https://demo.foxel.cc](https://foxel.cc) 体验 Foxel 部分功能。
translatedContent: > Visit [https://demo.foxel.cc](https://foxel.cc) to experience some features of Foxel.

originContent: > 管理员账号：`demo@foxel.cc` 密码: `foxel_demo`
translatedContent: > Admin account: `demo@foxel.cc` Password: `foxel_demo`

originContent: ## 🚀 部署指南
translatedContent: ## 🚀 Deployment Guide
> ⚠️ **Important Notice:**

originContent: > Foxel 目前处于早期开发阶段，适合**尝鲜体验**和功能测试。当前版本在升级过程中可能包含**破坏性变更**，暂不提供数据迁移流程，升级时需要**重新安装**。如需**长期稳定使用**，建议等待 **Preview 版本** 发布后再部署，届时将提供完善的自动化版本升级流程。
translatedContent: > Foxel is currently in early development, suitable for **trial experience** and feature testing. The current version may include **breaking changes** during upgrades and does not provide a data migration process; upgrading requires **reinstallation**. For **long-term stable use**, it is recommended to wait for the **Preview version** release, which will provide a complete automated version upgrade process.

originContent: Foxel 提供多种部署方式以满足不同场景需求：
translatedContent: Foxel offers multiple deployment methods to meet different scenario needs:

originContent: - 🐳 **Docker Compose 一键部署** - 推荐新手使用
translatedContent: - 🐳 **Docker Compose One-Click Deployment** - Recommended for beginners

originContent: - 🐋 **Docker 单容器部署** - 适合自定义数据库
translatedContent: - 🐋 **Docker Single Container Deployment** - Suitable for custom databases

originContent: - 🔧 **源码编译部署** - 开发者专用
translatedContent: - 🔧 **Source Code Compilation Deployment** - For developers only

originContent: 📖 **详细部署教程请访问：[https://foxel.cc/guide/getting-started.html](https://foxel.cc/guide/getting-started.html)**
translatedContent: 📖 **For detailed deployment tutorials, please visit: [https://foxel.cc/guide/getting-started.html](https://foxel.cc/guide/getting-started.html)**

originContent: ## 🤝 贡献指南
translatedContent: ## 🤝 Contribution Guide

originContent: 我们欢迎所有对 Foxel 感兴趣的开发者加入贡献，共同改进和提升这个项目。
translatedContent: We welcome all developers interested in Foxel to contribute and help improve and enhance this project.

originContent: |      步骤      | 说明                                                                                          |
translatedContent: |      Step      | Description                                                                                   |

originContent:
| **提交 Issue** | - 发现 Bug 或有建议时，请提交 Issue。
- 请详细描述问题及复现步骤，便于快速定位和修复。 |
translatedContent:
| **Submit Issue** | - Submit an issue if you find a bug or have suggestions.
- Please describe the problem and reproduction steps in detail to facilitate quick location and fixing. |

originContent:
| **贡献代码** | - Fork 本项目并创建新分支。
- 遵循项目代码规范。 |
translatedContent:
| **Contribute Code** | - Fork this project and create a new branch.
- Follow the project coding standards. |

originContent:
| **功能扩展** | - 欢迎参与以下重点功能开发：
• 更智能的图像检索算法
• 增强社交互动
• 云存储/网盘集成
• 更多智能图像处理方法（如自动标注、风格迁移、图像增强等） |
translatedContent:
| **Feature Expansion** | - Welcome to participate in the development of the following key features:
• Smarter image retrieval algorithms
• Enhanced social interaction
• Cloud storage/drive integration
• More intelligent image processing methods (e.g., automatic tagging, style transfer, image enhancement, etc.) |

originContent: 如有任何疑问或建议，欢迎通过 Issue 与我们联系。感谢您的贡献！
translatedContent: If you have any questions or suggestions, please feel free to contact us via Issue. Thank you for your contribution!
